<D>__{i'd say i'm behaving as professionally as anyone else in this town.}
<C>__{director}
<D>__{where were you?!}
<C>__{frances}
<D>__{terribly, terribly sorry; i overslept. what's the name of this fine entertainment we're all so involved in?}
